    {
      "date_stolen": 1733623200,
      "description": "I came outside this morning 12/7/24 to find my prized commuter had disappeared from my backyard. Near City Park and Mountain. Likely stolen in the night. It was a barn find that I rebuilt and added many non-stock parts parts to, and I haven't seen seen anything similar to it around town. Unfortunately I did not write down the serial number, but I will be filing reports with Bike Index and the city.\r\n\r\n~1994 Red Specialized Crossroads in XL/Large with White Decals\r\n\r\nUPANBIKE butterfly bars Wrapped in Red (Most Distinctive)\r\nBlack Avid Speed Dial Brake Levers\r\nKoski V-Brake front/ Avid Single Digit Rear Calipers\r\nNo-name 3x8 Speed Shifters\r\nShimano Deore LX Rear Derailleur\r\nVintage Shimano Exage? Front Derailleur\r\nPuroma Red Pedals\r\nBlack Easton Front Wheel - Specialized Sawtooth Tire\r\nDura-Ace Hub With Mavic Rim Rear Wheel - Goodyear Transit Speed Tire\r\nSilver Sunrace 11-40t Cassette on the Rear Wheel (Big Gear on back wheel)\r\nBontrager Seat\r\n\r\nOther Stuff:\r\n\r\nFaded Brown REI Flash Pannier on left side\r\nJim Blackburn Bottle Cage and JBlackburn Rear Rack\r\nAdjustable Bottle Cage on seat tube\r\nRockBros Tubetop Bag and Frame Bag\r\nPolar Colorado Water Bottle\r\nRed Phone Mount\r\nBlitzu Bike Light (Paint Heavily Faded)\r\nOnGuard U Lock (Unlocked)",
